      <div class="gf__post-content-title gf__post-content-title--medium gf__post-content-title--dark">
        <h1 class="lal-f2">
          <a href="https://lawliberty.org/we-can-do-better-than-the-framers-constitution/">We Can Do Better Than the Framers&#8217; Constitution</a>
        <h1>
      </div>

                        <div class="gf__post-content-authors gf__post-content-authors--dark">
      
    
    <span class="gf__post-content-authors-author lal-f2 lal-f2--small-caps lal-f2--semibold"><a href="https://lawliberty.org/author/francis-buckley/">F.H. Buckley</a></span>
    </div>
        
                <div class="gf__post-content-summary gf__post-content-summary--dark">
          <p class="lal-f2">Originalism is a form of legal positivism and as such is devoid of moral force, except as a covert method of subverting a dominant left-liberal tradition.</p>
        </div>
              
    </div>

