          <a href="https://lawliberty.org/adrian-vermeule-unwitting-new-originalist/">Adrian Vermeule: Unwitting New Originalist</a>
        <h1>
      </div>

                        <div class="gf__post-content-authors gf__post-content-authors--dark">
      
    
    <span class="gf__post-content-authors-author lal-f2 lal-f2--small-caps lal-f2--semibold"><a href="https://lawliberty.org/author/john-mcginnis/">John O. McGinnis</a></span>
    </div>
        
                <div class="gf__post-content-summary gf__post-content-summary--dark">
          <p class="lal-f2">Those who want space to pursue the common good in many of the ways that Vermeule promotes should be attracted to originalism.</p>
